Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在撤退下次有必胜的把握咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想在此壮烈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏瑞安 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥 真的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和强袭在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我为什么 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来捧场让我倍感荣幸 基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 不妨跟我来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 这也是你诞生的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人类无尽的欲望下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借进步之名 产下疯狂梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚者们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你也是 他们的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:06.31,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1176,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}大门打开
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.29,0:03:06.31,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1176,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}大门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是禁忌的圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以神自居的人们 梦想的残垣断壁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在的父亲 并非真正的血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说 你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怪他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的话也不可能这样长大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此无忧无虑 普普通通的长大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从阿斯兰口中听到你的名字时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未想到 你竟然就是“他”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为已经早早夭折了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和响博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是当时蓝色宇宙的头号暗杀对象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你活了下来…还长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经枪林弹雨洗礼仍存活至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是让我这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难免开始相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们曾经追求的那个疯狂的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你想说我是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人类的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为那个梦想 响博士开发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专用的人造子宫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是其中唯一的成功胚胎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在众多兄弟姐妹相继夭折后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说得的你也信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面港口外有三艘纳斯卡级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-1对付主天使那三架有点辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止有点！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝·克莱茵、巴尔菲鲁特队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 提亚哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉也一去不回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰请继续待命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 三架机体渺无音讯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以更需要你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能继续盲目分散兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主天使号何时再次发动攻击 无法预料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算基拉他们从此一去不回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我想现在公开我的秘密」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我并非通过自然受孕」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「来到这世界上的」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 那个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我在受精卵阶段」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「接受过人工基因改造」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类中最早的调整人 乔治·格兰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜他带来的混乱 最终造成多大的灾难？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们自那之后 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做了些什么你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛就蓝色吧 要金发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让孩子继承我的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高超的天赋是给孩子最好的馈赠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流产了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在搞什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得花大钱改造了基因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意妊娠中的营养摄取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活 也要遵照医嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能打保票的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母体是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体状况肯定会影响胎儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛的颜色不对啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出大价钱买来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都希望梦想成真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不希望承担失败的风险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的不确定因素是妊娠中的母体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要攻克这道难关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就要挑战它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了确保梦想不会流产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号机警报
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 提高过滤装置的功率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳上升 血压超过200
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是东西 是生命！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们必须将它付诸完善！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命是孕育而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人工制造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们最终获得了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看双手 看看梦想的尽头！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子 还我…把那孩子还我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要另一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用最前沿的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他成为最强大的调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蓝色纯净的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蓝色纯净的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蓝色纯净的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强的调整人…那样他就会幸福了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求更高更强更好 这是人类进步的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是因为那是幸福之源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇 贪婪 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终却忘记最初是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口口声声爱护生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却玩弄生命互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个调整人 别来套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他们世界才会有混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经是 不同于自然人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个新的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得多少知识 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得多少技术也不会满足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿此次作战 使战争早期结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿真正的自由与正义昭之天下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就嫉妒、仇恨、相互残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿这些牺牲能够让战争早日结束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蓝色纯净的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就尽情地疯狂杀戮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足你们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 你有什么资格大放厥词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这宇宙中唯一一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有资格制裁全人类的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你妈的 这个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克隆是违法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法是人制订的 不会一成不变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦研究得到的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧 要多少研究资金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗 穆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在遥远的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未踏上战场时 曾有一面之缘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之遗产全部由他继承
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要那种女人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我从小严格管教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以那个傻小子作为前车之鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷和夫人还在里面！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 母亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个自认为有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以买来生命的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔达·弗拉戈的劣质克隆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离122 三艘纳斯卡级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下先行动者不利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 无法保证成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对着困难说不行谁都会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能战胜困难达到目的的才是优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在商界可是人人皆知的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是战场 失败意味着死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商界也一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别告诉我…你从来只打必胜之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过偶尔 也需要冒点风险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则是成不了胜利者的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人要有点上进心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出点魄力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说不入虎穴焉得虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以前强袭的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是和阿斯兰从小认识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没他们那样的觉悟和怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过亲眼看过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多尔…多尔都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙还活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过他们 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过阿拉斯加和巴拿马和奥布发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我回到扎夫特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当个只会服从命令打仗的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次失败了又会被骂？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 给那个大叔随便摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没辙 比起被杀还是杀人痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-131 确认APU分离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空 允许灾祸出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-252 前进准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主天使号 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿迪斯舰长 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 队长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸的克隆？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种童话故事 鬼才相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不愿意相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可惜的是 那是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主天使号出现 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离50 绿色B
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个热源接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对照热纹 是那三架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的大门即将打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将由我打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这世界也将结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个无尽欲望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里挣扎的傲慢者们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如他们所愿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们保护舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意纳斯卡级的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈特弗里德瞄准 装填科林斯飞弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮准备 反光束爆雷发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 就凭你们几个能有何作为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无人能够阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个席卷宇宙的仇恨风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 就一架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那早点打完收工吧 这次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈特弗里德 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹4 绿色A
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左转舵10
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克 听见吗 撤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果认为不是扎夫特的都是敌人就开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被骗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难说到底是谁被骗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难说 但我决定去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥 基拉 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈特弗里德 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避 舰首下沉俯角20
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护正义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「流星」还无法使用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分30秒后完成启动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的话 不想和你打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧 站得起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迂回到残骸后方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然没有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 是自由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆负伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！您怎么才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士队准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电告荷尔德林号和赫伊津哈号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能继续在一旁看着！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体 决不能让它落入地球军手里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也出击 准备CGUE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就上舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 轮到你帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的赌注
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系到大门是否打开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳斯卡级出现 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离80 蓝色D
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无人能够阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个席卷宇宙的仇恨风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三艘纳斯卡级正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说要把这女人怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 队长好像有什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你替我送去
